AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 63 Senior Resident Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 22, 2025, 10:21 IST
 All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Bhubaneswar
 63 Jobs |  Posted On : 22-Aug-2025 |  Odisha |  Salary : 67,700 to 67,700




FOLLOW

All India Institute of Medical Sciences Bhubaneswar (AIIMS Bhubaneswar) has announced the official notification for 2025. Those candidates who have qualified in the MD/ MS, DNB can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025. Here we mentioned the age limit, selection process, and salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can apply online through the website on or before the last date of application.




IIf you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Odisha.

AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Senior Resident 	63	MD/ MS, DNB

Age Limit for the AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 45 years.

Selection Process for the AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 67,700 /- per month.

Application fee for the AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025

For OBC candidates: Rs. 1,500 /-
For SC/ ST candidates: Rs. 1,200 /-
For PWBD candidates: Nil
How to Apply for the AIIMS Bhubaneswar Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Senior Resident Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Click on the Apply Online link.
Log in with your mobile number and password.
Fill out the given details carefully.
Pay the application fee (if applicable)
Submit the application form and take a printout of the application form for further reference.

Important Dates

Starting Date of Application	 18-08-2025
Last Date of Application	02-09-2025
